Following the release of the album Justin at the end of September, singer-songwriter Justin Lo held the Air Justin 08 Live concert series in Hong Kong in October, which was then taken to Guangzhou and Kuala Lumpur. The set list included new songs "Haven't Lost Yet" and "Thirty Days", plus past popular picks Kong, Volar, Erica, "Good Guy", "I Ain't a Good Guy", "Man, KTV", and "This Day, Every Year" (duet with Leo Ku). These are all collected here on two DVDs totaling 29 tracks.



Audio 1 : Dolby Digital Stereo Karaoke
Audio 2 : Dolby Digital 5.1 Concert Vocal
